    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<h2>Councilman Ortwell Brane — Architect of Closure</h2>\n<p><em>Mid-fifties. Sponsored the Civic Reconciliation Closure motion; it passed 4–3 and is in its mandatory fourteen-day review period when Phase 5 opens. Not corrupt. Not E.'s asset. The conspiracy's most useful weapon in Loftwick is his honest belief that public order outweighs continuing inquiry.</em></p>\n<h3>Combat behavior</h3>\n<p><strong>None.</strong> Will not initiate violence under any circumstances Phase 5 contemplates.</p>\n<h3>Statblock summary (CR 1/2, PB +2)</h3>\n<p>AC 12 · HP 31 (7d8) · Speed 30 ft. · Init +1 · Passive Perception 13</p>\n<p>STR 11 · DEX 12 · CON 13 · INT 15 · WIS 16 · CHA 16. Saves: WIS +5, CHA +5. Skills: History +4, Insight +5, Persuasion +5.</p>\n<h3>Source</h3>\n<p><em>Blooming Rot, Part 2 — Phase 5.</em> See <em>Phase 5 — Loftwick NPCs → Ortwell Brane — Architect of Closure</em> for the three tactics that can succeed against him.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
